components.content: Remember that older elephants can teach younger elephants (this is you using your memory!).
If a group of elephants go near a hive,
the guard bees fly out of the hive.
The buzzing noise scares the older elephants.
They warn the other elephants by making a
rumbling noise and then run away.
The young elephants hear the bees buzzing
They see the older elephants run away and also
